data.description: Welcome to this stunning upper-level condo with a dramatic vaulted ceiling and gleaming hardwood floors! This 2 bedroom, 1 bath home features classic appointments throughout. You will love the two large bedrooms. The serene primary bedroom boasts a bay window and ceiling fan. The newer sliding glass door leads to a private 11x9 deck with a storage area that overlooks mature trees. The kitchen is the ideal place for entertaining with a large breakfast bar and double sink. The dining room is filled with an abundance of natural light. The spacious great room is the perfect place to relax. Newer windows and the HVAC is only 10 years old. The laundry room is just off of the kitchen! This sought-after location puts you close to shopping, restaurants, and the Page extension. Assigned parking spot in front of the building for your convenience and ample parking for guests. This is the condo you have been waiting for!
